We are **Ramper**, an experimental musical project born in Granada, Spain.

Our music explores the boundaries of slowcore, post-rock, and ambient, aiming to create sonic landscapes that are both heavy and ethereal.

> "The second album, Solo Postres (2024), received coverage in national mainstream press and has cultivated a dedicated cult following within the Spanish independent, slowcore, and post-rock scenes."

Formed by close friends and unified by a specific sonic vision. 
